Key Match Events: Jasprit Bumrah returned to international cricket after a year out due to injury and struck twice in his first over in the first T20I against Ireland.
Bumrah dismissed Balbirnie with a full delivery that took the inside edge onto the stumps.
Bumrah took his second wicket by dismissing Tucker, who attempted to ramp a length ball but only managed to spoon it behind to Sanju Samson.
